            <description><![CDATA[可以参考此处一键部署 running-on-railway]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>可以参考此处一键部署 <a href="https://umami.is/docs/running-on-railway" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">running-on-railway</a><br>
<!-- -->但是我这边选择的是使用docker镜像在Railway上部署  </p></blockquote><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="创建一个gitthub项目">创建一个gitthub项目<a class="hash-link" href="#创建一个gitthub项目" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2><p>新建一个Dockerfile</p><div class="language-dockerfile codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-dockerfile codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token instruction keyword" style="color:#00009f">FROM</span><span class="token instruction"> ghcr.io/mikecao/umami:postgresql-v1.31.0</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token instruction keyword" style="color:#00009f">ARG</span><span class="token instruction"> PORT</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token instruction keyword" style="color:#00009f">ARG</span><span class="token instruction"> DATABASE_TYPE postgresql</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token instruction keyword" style="color:#00009f">ARG</span><span class="token instruction"> DATABASE_URL</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token instruction keyword" style="color:#00009f">ARG</span><span class="token instruction"> HASH_SALT</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="去railway上新建一个项目">去railway上新建一个项目<a class="hash-link" href="#去railway上新建一个项目" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2><p><em>todo</em></p>]]></content:encoded>
